Green is the new black in the mobility universe. And Telepass is bringing sustainability to Web3. Make the most of our members-only benefits on Web3 and the in real world with the EV Charging NFT. 

Don't forget to link your Telepass Plus account to your NFTLP to enjoy our full range of benefits. 

Visit https://www.telepass.com/en/consumer/services/electric-charging for more details.
